snippet.title: Edward Riordan
snippet.description: My name is Edward Riordan and I am a trained remote viewer. This YOUTUBE page is to support my website www.erviewer.com. I record my session on video for the world to see. Remote viewing is a perceptual art form to access information about a person, place, thing or event anywhere in time or space. In all of my sessions, I do not know what the target it, I am essentially "blind" to the target. I hope you enjoy these videos, I plan on creating many many more. Please support my work with a donation at https://www.paypal.me/EdwardRiordan
